author: The Current
description:
To celebrate The Current’s 20th Anniversary, The Current’s Live Sessions Vault unlocks never-before-seen live performance videos of bands and artists who have played in our iconic studio. 

Watch to see the full session of The Cactus Blossoms featuring previously unreleased footage, from when they visited The Current studio back in 2016.

Songs Performed 
00:00:00 I Could Never Get Tired
00:04:02 Sooner or Later
00:07:24 Why? (Lonnie Mack cover)

Musicians
Page Burkum — vocals, guitar
Jack Torrey — vocals, guitar
Tyler Burkum — vocals, guitar
Andy Carroll — bass
Chris Hepola — drums

Credits
Engineer – Michael DeMark
Producer – Andrea Swensson
Visuals  – Nate Ryan
Digital Producer – Natalia Toledo
Graphics – Natalia Toledo

The Current’s Live Sessions Vault is supported by the Minnesota Orchestra, GS Motors, and Delta Dental of Minnesota Foundation.
